des:
Ask for Psychological Facts, and learn about what really matters, like psychological matter.

Psychological Facts provides some interesting facts to people as well as helps them in understanding people.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Psychological Facts" or "Alexa, open Psychological Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"

This skill is compatible with the bluetooth devices, headphones, Alexa devices
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
